There are currently no commercial options available to return to the UK from Niger. All international passenger flights into and out of Niger have been suspended and the airports remain closed until further notice.
We know this is concerning for British people trying to leave Niger. The UK government is working closely with airlines, the Nigerien authorities and other governments to make sure options are available for you to return to the UK as soon as possible.
If you cannot leave Niger at this time, see information on staying in Niger during coronavirus.
Future travel options
The UK government is working closely with airlines, the Niger authorities and other governments to make sure options are available for you to return to the UK as soon as possible.
This travel advice will be updated when departure options become available.
